			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Never mind, I found it:
<br />

<br />
In hotproperty.html.php
<br />
Find the function show_EmailForm (line 906)
<br />
Place the include statement directly below the end of the html for the form, like this:
<br />

<br />
&lt;/form&gt;
<br />
&lt;?php
<br />
include_once ( 'bbantispam.php' );
<br />
}
<br />

<br />
Don't know if this is good programming, but it does work. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
